&lt;li&gt;Contribute across the stack—from front-end UI to back-end infrastructure—to develop new features, fix bugs, and optimize performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dive into possibly unfamiliar areas like Python notebooks, VS Code plug-ins, and containerized environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
